In a 4 quart, microwave-safe dish, combine butter, garlic and onion. Microwave on HIGH for 3 minutes. Place RED GOLD(R) or REDPACK(R) DICED TOMATOES with BASIL, GARLIC & OREGANO in the dish. Microwave until hot but not boiling, 2 minutes. Stir in the rice; cover and microwave on HIGH for 6 minutes. Stir in RED GOLD(R) or REDPACK(R) TOMATO SAUCE and microwave on HIGH for an additional 10 to 12 minutes or until liquid is gone. Stir in cheese and serve.